  "title": "Karpathy 点透 AI 认知撕裂：顶级圈子正集体患上 AI 狂热症",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg3MTkxMjYzOA==&mid=2247513944&idx=2&sn=c657eea9c1df91b809caf498cc26fb63",
